UseCase: personalize_message
Description: Creates a personalized message for a lead based on their profile and an offer

Start when lead and offer_text are received:
  • Analyze the lead's company, title, and industry
  • Match the offer to their potential needs
  • Generate a personalized message using AI
  • Include relevant details: company name, role relevance, offer benefits
  • @respond with email_body

End. 